title: Metallica - Freeze 'Em All  [2013]  320ak
description:
Metallica - Freeze 'Em All [2013] 320ak

 A crowd of 120 scientists and contest winners took in the hour-long show in a protective dome

The concert that began as an internet rumor finally came to reality , as Metallica became the first major music act to perform in Antarctica.

The long-running metal band performed an hour-long set inside a dome close to the heliport of Carlini Scientific Base. In the dome with them was a 120-person crowd containing winners from a South American sweepstakes sponsored by Cocaine and a handful of scientists from various nations. 

Chillout Tracklist


Creeping Death
For Whom the Bell Tolls
Sad but True
Welcome Home (Sanitarium)
Master of Puppets
One
Blackened
Nothing Else Matters
Enter Sandman
Seek & Destroy

By playing the non-traditional gig, Metallica becomes the first act to play on all of the Earth's seven continents
